"><div class="media-object-video"><div class="wsj-media-summary clearfix"><div class="strap-container"><h4 class="strap" itemprop="description"></h4></div></div><iframe width="400" height="225" src="https://video-api.wsj.com/api-video/player/v3/iframe.html?guid=F8CAFD10-50A3-4EFF-A518-805D9740736F&amp;height=225&amp;width=400&amp;plid=video_amp&amp;chainVideos=true&amp;parentUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2Fdevon-archer-testimony-transcript-house-oversight-hunter-biden-joe-biden-ukraine-a21915bc&amp;a=a" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></iframe><p class="imageCaption">亨特·拜登的前商业伙伴德文·阿彻 (Devon Archer) 向众议院监督委员会闭门作证，讲述总统与其子的海外商业交易的关系，其中包括与商业伙伴通过免提电话进行了 20 多次通话。图片：路透社/美联社 综合：马克·凯利<span class="imageCredit">华尔街日报互动版</span></p></div></div></section></div></main></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 04 Aug 2023 13:26:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/devon-archer-testimony-transcript-house-oversight-hunter-biden-joe-biden-ukraine-a21915bc</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/devon-archer-testimony-transcript-house-oversight-hunter-biden-joe-biden-ukraine-a21915bc<author><![CDATA[The Editorial Board]]></author><category>政治/一般新闻</category><category>政治/国际关系</category><category>国内政治</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论/意见</category><category>法激活过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category><category>SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>德文郡弓箭手</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>亨特·拜登</category><category>政治的</category><category>一般新闻</category><category>政治</category><category>国际关系</category><category>国内政治</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论</category><category>意见</category><category>法蒂瓦过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category></item></channel></rss>